</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-118_">Maintains a searchable public register.
</li></ul><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-120_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-68bd43bb-be40-4046-9384-99bfbd701bb8"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><strong>5.&nbsp;General Optical Council (GOC)</strong>
