</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-138_">Maintains professional standards in musculoskeletal care.
</li></ul><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-140_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-8aefb054-a822-4d0a-bb34-04fc9447ede5"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><strong>7.&nbsp;General Chiropractic Council (GCC)</strong>
